trans-unit.source: Defines custom placement parameters for a <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Definierar placeringen av anpassade parametrar för en <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup"> </xref> kontroll.

trans-unit.source: The CustomPopupPlacement structure defines a location for a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup> control with respect to its parent, and defines how the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup> moves to become more visible when it is obscured by a screen boundary.
trans-unit.target: Strukturen CustomPopupPlacement definierar en plats för en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup>styr med avseende på dess överordnade och definierar hur <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup>flyttar ska bli tydligare när det döljs av en skärm gräns.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.CustomPopupPlacementCallback?displayProperty=fullName> delegate returns an array of these structures as custom placement options for a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup> when the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup.Placement%2A> property is set to <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.PlacementMode>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.CustomPopupPlacementCallback?displayProperty=fullName>delegat returnerar en matris med dessa strukturer som anpassade placeringsalternativ för en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup>när <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup.Placement%2A>egenskapen <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.PlacementMode>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.PlacementMode> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup.Placement%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.CustomPopupPlacementCallback?displayProperty=fullName>
